<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Tracking Sheet Template</h2>

<p>Most tournament players use a pre-printed tracking sheet with all 26 letters and their counts. As each letter appears on the board, they cross off one instance. Here's what a mid-game tracking sheet reveals:</p>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-blue-500/30 bg-blue-950/20">
  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">💡 Mid-Game Example</p>
  <p class="text-base text-gray-200">After 10 turns, if your tracking shows <span class="text-white font-medium">all 4 S tiles played</span>, you know no one can pluralise a word for the rest of the game. If <span class="text-white font-medium">both blanks are gone</span>, bingo probability drops sharply for everyone.</p>
</div>

